                    "company": "Tony's Chocolonely",
                    "description": "As a key member of the leadership team, I play a pivotal role in driving the company's purpose, impact and sustainability goals during a rapid international expansion phase. During this transformative period, I successfully established the impact team and formulated a comprehensive sustainability strategy. My primary objective has been to cultivate a highly proficient team and implement effective programs to bring the purpose of Tony's Chocolonely to life.\n\nKey achievements:\n\u2022\tClosing living income gaps for 20,000 cocoa farmers, reducing child labor from 45% to less than 5%. Implemented measures to achieve full farm-level traceable cocoa sourcing, zero deforestation, complete carbon footprint disclosure, and innovative offsetting and reduction programs.\n\u2022\t5x winner of the Sustainable Brand Award. Achieved B-corp top-score of 125.\n\u2022\tSpearheaded the establishment and growth of an international team, expanding from two to fifteen members across Amsterdam, Ghana, and C\u00f4te d'Ivoire. Demonstrated strong adaptability and cultural sensitivity while working collaboratively in remote and diverse environments.\n\u2022\tDeveloped industry-leading sustainability programs, generating substantial improvements in cocoa farmer incomes, eradicating child labour and ending deforestation.\n\u2022\tPioneered the creation of Tony's Open Chain, a collaborative platform that has garnered participation from over twelve other chocolate companies, including Albert Heijn and Ben&Jerry's. This initiative seeks to amplify our collective impact.\n\u2022\tInspired and coached the entire Tony's team to align their work with the company's purpose, fostering a strong sense of connection in a rapidly expanding organization (from 45 to 280 employees).\n\u2022\tEstablished and oversaw a comprehensive reporting framework for non-financial KPIs, climate footprint, and net-zero commitment. Additionally, initiated and facilitated the development of an independent third-party assurance for our renowned sustainability report.",
